 class=\"toc-text\">2.1 文件类型绕过</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-2-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B4%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.2 文件头绕过</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-3-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%90%8E%E7%BC%80%E5%90%8D%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.3 文件后缀名绕过</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.配合文件包含漏洞</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4-%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4.配合服务器解析漏洞</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#5-%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">5.配合操作系统文件命令规则</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#6-CMS%E3%80%81%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">6.CMS、编辑器漏洞</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#7-%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">7.配合其他规则</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%890x00%E6%88%AA%E6%96%AD%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%8E%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">（1）0x00截断：基于一个组合逻辑漏洞造成的，通常存在于构造上传文件路径的时候</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89-htaccesss\"><span class=\"toc-text\"